folder: Willow St. & Pineapple St., Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1)
79-85 Willow Street; at the S.E. corner of Pineapple Street. From left to right, are the homes of Samuel Rowland and of one Kaltenborn. In 1925, both houses were acquired by the Sabine Realty Co., from the Estate of Samuel Rowland, and they, in 1929, erected a 15-story apartment house on the sites.

1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, another angle.

April 1925.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3)
The same, another view.

April 1925.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
